00:32:08.519 --> 00:32:10.519
Makakarating pa rin ba tayo sa Rain Manor sa tamang oras?

00:32:11.319 --> 00:32:11.799
Bizhi,

00:32:12.160 --> 00:32:13.960
pwede ba tayong maglakad papunta doon?

00:32:14.119 --> 00:32:15.839
Kung wala kang pakialam, sige lang.

00:32:16.319 --> 00:32:18.319
Maghihintay ako ng masasakyan dito.

00:32:19.079 --> 00:32:20.720
Susunduin ka namin sa daan.

00:32:20.880 --> 00:32:21.400
Pumunta.

00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:24.559
Ayusin mo 'yan agad, kung gayon.

00:32:28.039 --> 00:32:28.599
Tumigil!

00:32:28.720 --> 00:32:29.279
Tumigil!

00:32:36.519 --> 00:32:37.240
Kumusta, ginoo.

00:32:37.559 --> 00:32:38.599
Nasira lang ang sasakyan namin.

00:32:38.759 --> 00:32:40.000
Kung ito ay maginhawa para sa iyo,

00:32:40.000 --> 00:32:41.559
Maaari mo ba kaming ihatid papuntang Rain Manor?

00:32:41.560 --> 00:32:42.790
Pupunta ka rin ba sa Rain Manor?

00:32:42.880 --> 00:32:43.839
Ikaw rin?

00:32:43.839 --> 00:32:44.319
Oo.

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:45.559
(Pan Yunzhe)
Sabay na tayo.

00:32:45.759 --> 00:32:46.519
(Pan Yunzhe)
Matutuwa si Elder Yu

00:32:46.599 --> 00:32:47.440
(Pan Yunzhe)
para makita ang pagdating ng lahat sa oras.

00:32:47.640 --> 00:32:48.200
Salamat.

00:32:48.880 --> 00:32:49.720
Bizhi,

00:32:50.079 --> 00:32:51.240
nakasakay kami.

00:32:52.480 --> 00:32:53.119
Mabilis.

00:32:59.680 --> 00:33:00.160
Mga ginoo.

00:33:00.599 --> 00:33:01.519
(Pan Jingting)
Ito ang aking ama.

00:33:04.079 --> 00:33:05.039
Kumusta, ginoo.

00:33:05.039 --> 00:33:05.720
Ikinagagalak kong makilala ka.

00:33:26.100 --> 00:33:28.900
(Manor ng Ulan)

00:33:46.119 --> 00:33:46.920
Ginoong Pan.

00:33:47.319 --> 00:33:48.000
Ginang Wu.

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:48.960
Matagal na tayong hindi nagkikita.

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:50.599
Mas gumanda ka ngayon kaysa dati.

00:33:51.480 --> 00:33:52.400
Tara na.

00:33:52.519 --> 00:33:54.480
Hindi ka man lang dumalo sa performance ko.

00:33:54.640 --> 00:33:56.720
May gwapo ka na

00:33:57.400 --> 00:33:58.119
asawa,

00:33:59.559 --> 00:34:00.920
kaya wala kang oras para sa akin.

00:34:02.599 --> 00:34:03.279
Elder Pan.

00:34:03.279 --> 00:34:04.000
Kumusta.

00:34:04.599 --> 00:34:05.200
Ginang Wu.

00:34:06.440 --> 00:34:07.319
Nagkikita tayong muli.

00:34:07.720 --> 00:34:09.000
Salamat sa pagpunta mo noong gabing iyon.

00:34:09.000 --> 00:34:09.679
Wala lang 'yon.

00:34:10.000 --> 00:34:11.500
Salamat din sa tulong mo, Bb. Wu.

00:34:12.679 --> 00:34:13.519
Ito ang aking asawa.

00:34:14.960 --> 00:34:15.599
Wei Zhuoran.

00:34:15.880 --> 00:34:16.480
Bizhi.

00:34:16.880 --> 00:34:17.559
Su Beilu.

00:34:19.000 --> 00:34:20.639
Magkakilala ba kayo?

00:34:20.719 --> 00:34:21.360
Nagkita na tayo.

00:34:26.960 --> 00:34:28.199
Ang magkapatid na Hong iyon.

00:34:28.559 --> 00:34:29.119
Gumastos.

00:34:30.119 --> 00:34:30.800
Magsinungaling.

00:34:32.900 --> 00:34:34.199
Hayaan mong ipakilala ko ang dalawang ito.

00:34:34.639 --> 00:34:36.320
Sila ang mga anak ng pinsan ni Elder Yu,

00:34:36.330 --> 00:34:38.840
at mga pinuno ng pinakamalaking
sentro ng martial arts sa rehiyon,

00:34:38.840 --> 00:34:40.719
Sentro ng Sining Militar sa Hong.

00:34:41.000 --> 00:34:41.599
Hong Lie.

00:34:42.079 --> 00:34:42.760
Hong Chi.

00:34:42.760 --> 00:34:43.480
(Hong Chi, Hong Lie)

00:34:43.480 --> 00:34:44.119
(Hong Chi, Hong Lie)
Natutuwa ka sa akin.

00:34:44.320 --> 00:34:45.320
Ang kapatid kong si Hong Lie

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:46.960
ay ang nag-iisang pinuno ng sentro.

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:49.000
Hindi ako sapat na may kakayahan para gawin iyon.

00:34:49.440 --> 00:34:50.719
Ikinagagalak kong makilala ka.

00:34:50.800 --> 00:34:51.480
Guro Hong.

00:34:53.119 --> 00:34:55.280
Paano ninyo nakilala si Mr. Pan?

00:34:56.079 --> 00:34:57.880
Nagkita tayo habang papunta rito.

00:34:57.880 --> 00:34:59.360
Sinakay niya kami.

00:35:00.880 --> 00:35:01.840
Nagkita na ba kayo ngayon lang?

00:35:02.599 --> 00:35:04.280
Kung ganoon, kailangan ko silang ipakilala sa iyo.

00:35:05.519 --> 00:35:07.239
Ito ang ama ni Yunzhe,

00:35:07.239 --> 00:35:09.400
Ang Textile King, Pan Jingting.

00:35:09.559 --> 00:35:11.119
Siya ay isang matandang kaibigan ni Elder Yu.

00:35:11.360 --> 00:35:13.280
Ang pinaka-kaakit-akit na ginoo dito

00:35:13.360 --> 00:35:15.239
Siya dapat si Yunzhe.

00:35:15.519 --> 00:35:17.079
Saanman siya magpunta,

00:35:17.079 --> 00:35:18.119
Hindi ka makakakita ng malamig na grupo ng mga tao.

00:35:18.159 --> 00:35:19.119
Tama, Bb. Wu?

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:22.159
Manor ng Ulan.

00:35:23.800 --> 00:35:25.159
Ilang taon na rin mula noong huli tayong dumating.

00:35:26.079 --> 00:35:26.880
Oo.

00:35:28.119 --> 00:35:30.760
Ilang taon na rin mula noong huli ko siyang nakita.

00:35:31.320 --> 00:35:33.159
Sana ay maayos ang kalagayan niya.

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:36.639
Elder Yu

00:35:39.199 --> 00:35:40.639
Hindi niya tayo nakalimutan, 'di ba?

00:35:40.940 --> 00:35:45.220
(Manor ng Ulan)

00:36:35.340 --> 00:36:39.540
(Nakatatanda Yu)

00:36:40.519 --> 00:36:41.639
Xiuyun.

00:36:43.599 --> 00:36:45.480
